{"TopicId":182162,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"Opportunity Eulogy","CreatedByName":"Mars-Bound Hokie","CreatedById":192121,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T05:22:11Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Mars-Bound Hokie","CreatedById":192121,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T05:22:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nI would like to give this eulogy to probably the greatest feat of space travel engineering yet, Opportunity.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nFrom the moment you first made contact on the Martian surface, everyone knew you were destined for greatness.\u00A0You were meant to last only 90 days, but you pressed on for 15 years. During that time, you collected a treasure trove of knowledge on the Red Planet - opening up new doors to science and engineering. Since that fateful day in 2018, we never gave up on you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nMay your contributions pave the way for more great feats in the future.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022SjQRzZE.jpg\u0022 height=\u0022415\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/SjQRzZE.jpg\u0022 style=\u0022border-style:none;vertical-align:middle;\u0022 width=\u0022601\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:26px;\u0022\u003E\u0022My battery is low and it\u0027s getting dark\u0022 (Opportunity\u0027s final words)\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nIf anyone else would like to pay respects, or have anything to say about Opportunity, don\u0027t hesitate to reply to\u00A0this thread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaverickSawyer","CreatedById":11952,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T05:40:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClear skies and following (and gentle) winds, Opportunity.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"scottadges","CreatedById":174580,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T06:23:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m sad to say I had forgotten about Opportunity. It seems so long now that it was running, like it would just go on forever.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s hoping in about 100 years... somebody walks out of their Mars Hab and takes a little drive out onto the dunes to find it, dust it off, and bring it back home.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mars-Bound Hokie","CreatedById":192121,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T06:32:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223540443\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550125414\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022174580\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022scottadges\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, scottadges said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s hoping in about 100 years... somebody walks out of their Mars Hab and takes a little drive out onto the dunes to find it, dust it off, and bring it back home.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf we put our minds to it, we can cut it down to 20 years.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T06:36:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFarewell, Opportunity.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://xkcd.com/2111/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://xkcd.com/2111/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T08:15:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd as such, ends the programmes of Mars Exploration Rovers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRather than saying \u0022Rest in Peace\u0022, I\u0027d rather say,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDona Nobis Pacem\u003C/strong\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMay we continue our future explorations in peace, and may our future explorations brings us peace.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-02-14T08:16:57Z\u0022 title=\u002202/14/2019 08:16  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 14, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by YNM\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T08:34:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nOPPORTUNITY\u003Cbr\u003E\nBorn: 2003\u003Cbr\u003E\nRested: 2019\u003Cbr\u003E\nReseted: 204?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-02-14T08:35:36Z\u0022 title=\u002202/14/2019 08:35  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 14, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Epicdreamer","CreatedById":167797,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T12:23:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d say only the Voyagers exceed Opportunity\u0027s exceptional design quality and endurance.\u00A0I remember being glued to the screen when he and his brother Spirit landed on\u00A0Mars. Shame to see Opportunity move to only memories. Exceptional machine. RIP...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbolExplorer","CreatedById":177191,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-14T15:48:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPress f to pay respect.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EF\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"magnemoe","CreatedById":57801,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-15T03:04:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223540602\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550159326\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022177191\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KerbolExplorer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, KerbolExplorer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPress f to pay respect.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EF\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nF\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xd the great","CreatedById":188222,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-15T08:52:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223540602\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221550159326\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022177191\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KerbolExplorer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, KerbolExplorer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPress f to pay respect.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EF\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen this message gets deleted because of \u0022suspected foul language\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-15T10:44:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLet\u0027s just create an Opportunity forum account with one (locked) post and start liking that post.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen the future students find and revive Opportunity, it will be very glad to see it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nP.S.\u003Cbr\u003E\nWe can do this for other lost crafts as a robot memorial.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-02-15T10:46:52Z\u0022 title=\u002202/15/2019 10:46  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 15, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Duck McFuddle","CreatedById":188882,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-16T17:27:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGoodbye, Opportunity... I never saw your landing, but I grew up hearing about your feats. You were one of the driving forces early on for my interest in space. I won\u0027t forget how you shaped my learning and understanding\u00A0of Mars, space, and science in general.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nR.I.P Opportunity\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tw1","CreatedById":59717,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-18T00:54:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:72px;\u0022\u003EF\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s amazing to me seeing the wide range of places talking about it, and so many people morning it. Opportunity was clearly widely loved.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-02-18T01:25:34Z\u0022 title=\u002202/18/2019 01:25  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 18, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Tw1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VQkr","CreatedById":195583,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-20T00:19:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOur space probes are the new adventurers, being sent to frontiers that humans may not visit for many decades. They are endearing to us in a way that few, if any, non-humanoid robots can be. Oppy, thanks for capturing the imaginations of so many earthlings!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Space Nerd","CreatedById":198691,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-20T10:51:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(A year later)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Comic Sans MS\u0027, cursive;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:72px;\u0022\u003EF\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}